  "text": "Cellular processes, such as transcription and translation, chromatin remodeling and pathwayspecific regulation, are sources of stochastic events leading to cell-to-cell variability [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . In fact, cellular behaviour varies in clonal cell populations despite their development in identical environments [CITATION_3] .",
